1. *Oblik* njene haljine je bio veoma neobičan. (The shape of her dress was very unusual.)
2. *Obliku* je dao mnogo pažnje. (He paid a lot of attention to the shape.)
3. Ona je *oblikovala* sliku svoje mašte. (She shaped the picture of her imagination.)
4. To je neobičan *oblik*. (That is an unusual shape.)
5. On je uvek bio dobar u *oblikovanju* predmeta. (He was always good at shaping objects.)